Resource Profile: openIMIS ActivityDefinition

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-activity-definition Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISActivityDefinition

Defines a ActivityDefinition for openIMIS which maps to a Medical Service.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Item Reference (Claim)
  • Examples for this Profile: A1

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
